data.description: Don't miss this exquisite 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom sanctuary nestled in a tranquil neighborhood. It boasts a luxurious owner's suite, a stamped patio, and backyard firepit/garden, all contributing to an idyllic living experience.Inside, you'll find solid surface floors throughout, complemented by a cozy fireplace and an open layout that allows natural light to flood the living spaces.Convenience and practicality are at the forefront with a two-car garage, updated utilities, and a partially finished basement.The private backyard, safely fenced in, features the centerpiece - a stamped concrete patio. This outdoor oasis is perfect for relaxation, entertainment, and al-fresco dining, where cherished memories will be made.
